body:
I was playing around on the PBE then I came up with a silly Leona build. But I think it could work. (If there are any, pro players who are willing to test it for fun on a draft game and give me feedback that would be great. I will be testing it too.)

The build is kinda late game-ish, and I found on the PBE that a full combo, R-W-Q-E-Ignite-AAx4 dealt about 3800 Magic damage with a full build. While still remaining tanky, thanks to the armor, Mr, and her W.

